The paper deals with logical formalization and proof in Coq, which suggests it belongs to the Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses program extraction and certification, which could also place it in the Programming Languages (cs.PL) and Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-categories. The use of Herbrand trees and counter-examples could also suggest a connection to Machine Learning (cs.LG) or Symbolic Computation (cs.SC).
